      • getUID

        java.lang.String getUID()
        The uid that describes this specific dataset provider. It is highly recommended that this uid is immutable for the lifespan of this dataset provider. It is up to the provider to distribute changes to the dataset provider under the same uid if the do not break previous compatibility.
        Returns:
        the uid for the dataset provider
